headline: Microsoft Corp (MSFT) Patches SharePoint Vulnerability amid Global Havoc
summary: Microsoft Corporation (NASDAQ:MSFT) is one of the best 52-week high stocks to buy now. On July 21, the software giant released a patch for a vulnerability that affected the servers of the SharePoint document management software. The patch addressed a loophole that hackers used to breach the networks of governments, businesses, and other organizations worldwide […]
